Package edu.wpi.cs.jburge.SEURAT.reports

This package implements rationale reports (traceability matrix, rationale tree) that are accessed via the pull-down menu on the RationaleExplorer or in the tree.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
GenerateCandidatePatternsComposite This class presents the wizard GUI to the users to generate candidate patterns.
GenerateCandidatePatternsDisplay Deprecated. This class is no longer in use.
GenerateRationaleReport Confirms the users requested report and allows them to select what type of report they would like
OutputTraceabilityMatrix Used to output a traceability matrix.
PreviewRationaleReport Constructs a preview of the rationale tree report that the user can view.
RationaleReportGenerator A Report Generator Object Will Create A Report For The Rationale.
TraceabilityMatrixDisplay Used to display the requirements traceability matrix, including requirements, alternatives, relationship type, and associated code.
